column5: For some reason the title 'Bungee cord snaps above crocodile-infested waters' got me chuckling pretty good!
Rutt row shaggy !!  Holy snapping bungee's batman.
lol that got a laught outta me too! and this is exactly whu i keep my a$$ on the ground where it belongs!
I don't feel anything either Simon    Adrenaline, maybe but I get that setting the hook on fish
I don't understand how any body could bungee jump...I just don't get it.
Damn, that looks amazing! Bungee jumping, cord snapping... going for a dip in crocodile infested waters... then swimming into the rapids. What could be better??
ZOINKS!!! It's the phantom croc Scoob!!!
after that a bad day at work just isn't important anymore, I bet
So the contest for the 2012 Darwin awards has begun!!
My son enjoyed bungee jumping, but then again he was also a fan of jumping out of perfectly good airplanes too.  Sure didn't get any of those traits from me though
I wonder if she got a refund ??? !!!!
To do it in a third world country..crazy!!! Some people just love the adrenelin rush......
Should have had her rod with her
Australia isn't a third world country. It is a first world.  Also some would say you have higher chances of an accident driving.
It happened in Zimbabwe...I wouldn't trust them.....
My appologies. These meds must be effecting me more then I realize lol. I could have swore it was Australia but nope. Saying that I wouldn't trust there gear neither.
It's all good...The inspections etc. couldn't possibly be up to the same standards we are used to....
That is forsure. Makes you wonder if they even inspect there stuff. I doubt that they have near the regs that we have.
The women was from Australia, but it happened in Zimbabwe.
